                "uuid": "0c1559b9-6d7e-4b96-8417-c08e52be1ccd",
                "control-id": "164.312(a)(1)",
                "description": "Access control — the Lambda IAM inline policy is replaced with a least-privilege policy granting only PutItem, GetItem, UpdateItem, Query on DynamoDB and PutObject, GetObject on the uploads path (GAP-07). The OPA policy blocks wildcard IAM actions in CI.",
